arStrings.szText: We first encountered it in skirmishes with Dregs. Not long after, it was being shared as a treatment for pain.
Kharov was the first to ritualize it. He enshrined it in our very faith, and I must admit, numbing absolution was attractive.
But, my hesitation gave me a clear mind as the Sacrament warped my brethren around me. I pray the Light returns to their worn faces.
